Responsibilities : 
DTS and MTS lead to backfill for a contractor. Must be willing to work with a Cannabis manufacturing client. Required skills and experiences: 
S/4HANA full implementation experience 
Strong team lead and communications skills 
Experience to direct and manage the client team and the off-shore CG team 
Experience in at least one of the following Consumer Packaged Goods industry / Food and Beverage / Pharmaceutical and Life Sciences 
Make-to-Stock manufacturing experience 
Willingness and capability to quickly learn and understand the clients unique business (Cannabis cultivation and manufacturing of Cannabis products, batch tracing, paying attention to quality management) 
Provide guidance to the MTS consultant on the team 
Familiar with Agile / iCaptivate Agile Hybrid implementation methodology. 
